interface.pattern:
test("Layer 3 RLS blocks cross-tenant access via direct SQL") {
  val tenantAConnection = dataSource.connection
  tenantAConnection.createStatement().execute("SET LOCAL app.tenant_id = 'tenant-a'")

  // Create widget for tenant-b via application
  createWidgetForTenant("tenant-b", widgetId)

  // Attempt direct SQL query as tenant-a → RLS blocks access
  val rs = tenantAConnection.createStatement()
    .executeQuery("SELECT * FROM widget_view WHERE id = '$widgetId'")

  rs.next() shouldBe false // RLS blocks: no results for tenant-b widget
}

standards.standard:
Use Testcontainers for PostgreSQL + Keycloak multi-service setup.
@DynamicPropertySource for dynamic connection configuration.
Shared containers across test class for performance (<3 min target).
